		["I guess your first exercise is going to be to mine your way down to the Undercity.  Heh, get it?  Mine... nevermind.  To get to the Undercity go to the rear of the Ruins of Lordaeron south of Brill, and take the elevator down.  Ask one of the Undercity Guardians there for further assistance."] = "2e97c78ba8df38524753f0708f9146cd",
		["You aiming to be a taxidermist?  I don't like people who think they can stuff and mount me because they think I'm dead.  No?  Good!  Look for Rand Rhobart at a camp to the southeast of town.  To get to him take the road southeast out of Brill and hang a left at the intersection."] = "b2057081f202c32ff47e8c3e643a50bf",
		["Black, grey and dark purple are the prescribed colors.  See to it that you don't stray onto the wrong side of fashion street friend.  Bowen Brisboise can help to see that you don't.  You'll find him inside Cold Hearth Manor on the other side of the bridge to the southwest of town."] = "d6769fe270aefb1f31493758e255cc9b",
		["What are you looking for?"] = "2496e7dedec4748fa10b50cbb971b275",
		["We don't have a bank here in Brill, you'll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions."] = "5adb08a671ae648047709221c58553c6",
		["There's a Bat Handler inside the Undercity.  Head south down the road out of Brill, then west at the T-intersection.  The Ruins of Lordaeron will be on your left.  Go into them and then down into the Undercity.  You can ask an Undercity Guardian there for further assistance."] = "7cde77346a7f6eeabaf54f17380e5d92",
		["You'll find Innkeeper Renee inside the Gallows' End Tavern at the southeast end of the street running through town."] = "e5750cf72eef1fd9a7b8998872a7898a",
		["Morganus the stable master can be found out in front of the stables strangely enough."] = "b3c7473fb751209da9ccc66fa335c622",
		["Which trainer do you seek?"] = "453b9c8037ce4d9e2cd70e18ad1d9620",
		["Which profession?"] = "68b0bdb01281865de220bb8ce19e964a",
		["You'll find the Mage Trainer, Cain Firesong, upstairs on the landing at the Gallows' End Tavern, which is on the southeast end of Brill.  I guess he checked in too late to get a room."] = "fd95ca0767fb6854229c17e46878eea4",
		["At the southeast edge of town is the Gallows' End Tavern.  Go there and head upstairs, and you'll find Dark Cleric Beryl inside the reading room."] = "5beef90fab0c2fbc8e782f8a205f7045",
		["The Rogue Trainer's name is Marion Call.  You can find her upstairs in the reading room at the Gallows' End Tavern at the town's southeast edge."] = "a3706807400a87a3d36b47b32c146081",
		["Rupert Boch is his name.  I hear that he's upstairs in one of the rooms at the Gallows' End Tavern on the southeast end of town."] = "de253e3169d9f7d6717bd3c610685772",
		["Look inside the Gallows' End Tavern's main dining room for Austil de Mon.  The tavern is on the southeast edge of Brill."] = "026418de080205834ee64ce5d0625a46",
		["Our Alchemist's name is Carolai Anise.  You'll find her in a house at the northwest end of Brill."] = "31cbfadfd213c0536a30ef65e2da9df4",
		["Sorry friend, we don't have one of those here in Brill.  You'll have to head to the Undercity for that.  The Undercity is underneath the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  From the back of the ruins take the elevator down and then speak to one of the Undercity Guardians to find your way further."] = "1d78372b655ebdea61f7c5f24bd72002",
		["Fancy yourself a chef?  Head to the Undercity south of town for your training.  You can catch the elevators heading down at the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron.  Talk to one of those lumbering Undercity Guardians for further assistance once you arrive."] = "3f03840f6cba54c94a171fec48a1899a",
		["You can find Vance Undergloom upstairs in a room at the Gallows' End Tavern on the southeast side of Brill."] = "93cc04c8b8e24496ad60223e82204b3c",
		["While there's no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions."] = "48bace730ef5ab4f593d6a3849c15245",
		["Nurse Neela greets all of her future customers as they enter the Gallows' End Tavern at the southeast end of town."] = "372f22b4f09e1c12985532736a35e6ef",
		["Clyde Kellen, the local bass master, has his favorite fishing spot just east of Brill at Brightwater Lake."] = "c8c457f00ba68e930345dc9a61425874",
		["Look for Faruza.  Last I saw she was standing out front between the stables and the house on the northwest end of town."] = "703653ea2b256edc8ff3ec853fb0791e",
		["That would be Shelene Rhobart.  Take the road southeast out of Brill then head east at the intersection.  She's at a camp along the side of the road."] = "d527ff651e5c8f5b38b73526706b5b23",
		["I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in the Undercity.  All you have to do to get there is head south out of town and go to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron.  Then take the elevator down into the Undercity itself and ask an Undercity Guardian for further directions."] = "9e32fc29d61e78d418bf12b83291d07c",
		["Rand Rhobart is fairly good at skinning felbats and the like.  You can find him at a camp along the road to the southeast of Brill.  Take the road southeast out of town and then head east at the intersection."] = "e4f311ec0b21740e615d6cb30e9cb438",
		["It is Bowen Brisboise that you seek then.  You'll find him inside his house southwest of Brill just on the other side of the bridge at Cold Hearth Manor."] = "a05a273555c4e438987174be83fe9a2d"
	},
	["Lady Katrana Prestor"] = {
		["<Lady Prestor glares at you.>"] = "c3be4e90159eac26604380da9c7a81ce",
		["I was standing right next to you, imbecile. I know what you seek."] = "a0f1f3ff9bb1cc58aeedfa5e124c36c4",
		["You seek to lower our global defenses in order to appease a paranoid magistrate and an encampment of riff-raff that are most probably suffering from heat stroke."] = "7280c9368c45e4d35c89e8e655616ae9"
	},
	["Tirion Fordring"] = {
		["Race does not dictate honor, $r. While you remain on my farmstead, I ask that you remember and respect this credo.$B$BI have known orcs who have been as honorable as the most noble of knights and humans who have been as vile as the most ruthless of Scourge.$B$BBut I shall not bore you with tales of my youth! There is much work to be done - if that is what you desire. "] = "da8d51ad6b190d0e4ebeee411858fb14",
		["Sit and listen to my story, $r."] = "9bbd45c8ec045ee83374773f963ec27c",
		["I must apologize for not being entirely truthful with you in regards to my identity. I had to be certain that you could be trusted - few people would have selflessly lent assistance to an old and forgotten hermit.$B$BYou have proven yourself as one of those people: A person of integrity and honor."] = "c140d7f6c311b75cf50828eb829cf9fd",
		["My son, Taelan, was only a child when I was found guilty of treason and banished from the Alliance to live a life in exile. I chose to remain here so that I could watch over him; to somehow insure that he would grow up an honorable man.$B$BAs I had hoped, he took my place as lord of Mardenholde; but in a cruel twist of fate, joined the ranks of the Scarlet Crusade. He is now their Highlord, $r."] = "9f1b29d378ef6d96e7efc0f960de367e"
	},
	["Kelstrum Stonebreaker"] = {
		["The big wars might be over, for now, but we still have to keep our skills sharp!"] = "ce85977b0f1b155023ca49641a927acd",
		["Yer no warrior... Why ye wouldn't even last a day under my training regimen!  $B$BA $c who thinks $ghe's : she's; a warrior.  Ha!"] = "64a04066374cb355ff1adeae11f4ae82",
		["Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned?"] = "31ab172e1a375db1c9157d594eb608d9"
	},
	["Stormwind City Patroller"] = {
		["Gryphons, eh? Never really cared for the beasts but to each their own.You can find Dungar Longdrink on the rampart in the Trade District."] = "258744fe85450f544093d5fd17856341",
		["Lookin' to take a gryphon ride, eh? Dungar keeps his birds up on the rampart in the Trade District. Just remember to hold on tight! "] = "7df84a254c23565acaa7fc468ead3ab2",
		["Ahhh, Stormwind Visitor's Center is what you are looking for then. It's the first building on the left as you walk through the front gates from the Valley of Heroes."] = "646cbbc2bf91bdaa020beb25f4e0a678",
		["A child of nature are we? Then you need look no further then the moonwell in the Park."] = "a63f0a77a472eab18caf48ea8320d27e",
		["Sounds like you want to talk to Maginor Dumas! You can usually find him in the Wizard's Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. Course, you never know when or where those magi will portal off to."] = "fa0d9c855011039c74c70b23db0b82ea",
		["I would suggest looking in the Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square."] = "7c15eb60533829779dc9fd0c60d26a6a",
		["Old Town is where you should go if you want to find rogues. It's in the northeast corner of Stormwind."] = "cd52082b0fdc76c7dded230c974a2ebf",
		["Check around Old Town at the Barracks or the Pig and Whistle Tavern. If you go to the tavern, be sure to sample some of the fine brews. Puts the dwarven ales to shame, I tell ya."] = "c621f0b9a4a6a6290dd5972a302122fc",
		["Another entrepreneur, eh? Well, the Auction House can be found in the Trade District.  Not far from the bank."] = "3b18fc0710278c6aa12fb30a85999aaf",
		["Stormwind Counting House is located by the front gates in the Trade District of Stormwind. And when you get tired of counting your money, be sure to stop by the Gilded Rose for a drink."] = "554b8726d09d342022c5c7eaf5a9818e",
		["You've heard about the Tram have you?  What a ride that thing is!  You'll find it in the Dwarven District towards the back.  Oh, and be sure to keep your arms and legs inside the tram while the tram is in motion."] = "98484e0cd95c72af21e16247f3eead70",
		["Ah, The Gilded Rose... with its soft down beds and warm baths... just thinking about that Inn makes me want to... ::yawn:: Lucky you if you're heading over there...  you will find it in the west side of the Trade District.   ...nice soft pillows, warm blankets.  ::yawn::"] = "e84a11ab6b3896ecf97c8adfbc08636c",
		["Ahhh, you are looking for Dungar Longdrink. He has some of the fastest gryphons this side of Khaz Modan! You can find him up on the ramparts in the Trade District."] = "a36856bf0646fdd5ce14e1bbdbeab7a2",
		["Gonna make a guild, are ya? Good luck to ya then!Talk to Aldwin Laughlin in the Stormwind Vistor's Center. It's in the Trade District right as you come in from the Valley of Heroes."] = "dbd178f951b41e05c59af921ec3b7725",
		["I don't know how they do it...  those mailboxes must be magic portals or something.  Why I see people gathered around the mailbox next to the bank all day pulling swords and shields and various armor all from that small box!"] = "b4b551dc6175faa3e32ad05a88b10b09",
		["If you need to house your pet while you're training another, then you should talk to Jenova Stoneshield over in the Dwarven District."] = "b68ea919378ae726f910e862a386d16f",
		["Master Woo Ping has mastered nearly every weapon known to man.  He is especially deadly with his sword techniques.  He spends a good deal of time over in the Weller's Arsenal waiting on new shipments of weapons to arrive if you need some training."] = "ea46258d498568523f3fadf071cc9af0",
		["Well, well, moving up in the world are we? You're looking for the Champions' Hall, and you'll find it on the southeast end of Old Town. If you're an officer you can enter the hall, otherwise you can still speak to Officer Areyn standing outside. Good luck!"] = "a0e2103ae01da9c6c1707056a504c6ae",
		["And I wish I could join you $n. Head over to Stormwind Keep. You'll find Thelman Slatefist in the King's audience chamber. He will aid you in getting to Alterac Valley."] = "5da822272073a4d726872184c3421ca6",
		["It's admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King's audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin."] = "adb9b1e902dc3d39490b7c0e4c0e67cd",
		["The Silverwing Sentinels can use all the help they can get in their fight against the Warsong Outriders. $n, go to Stormwind Keep and speak with Elfarran if you wish to assist them."] = "a28ad28e180fb23f6b2f30a8926dd8d3",
		["The Park is where you want to go if you are looking for druid trainers. Theridan and Maldryn can usually be found by the moonwell in the center of the district."] = "6ca4fdf838b083f58d40a21536adeaed",
		["A Hunter is it?  Well, then you will want to speak with Thorfin Stoneshield over in the Dwarven District.  Oh, and you be sure to tell him that if I step in his pet's business one more time, he's going to be training other hunters from behind bars in the Stockade!"] = "d9d6fc265ce7e558402d3ca53747dac5",
		["Oh, looking for some arcane enlightenment are you? No place better then then Wizard's Sanctum in the Mage Quarter."] = "0493aff58b480f500d524b265550d281",
		["Laurena is the High Priestess of Stormwind. You can find her in the Catheral of Light in Cathedral Square."] = "4a22a1b67aa8fe418d517ebb0e371796",
		["Bah, rogues have done nothing but make our job here in Stormwind harder. I wish I could drag both Osborne and Mathias both out of Old Town and right to the Stockade."] = "6e24adae0babfe7f1e128960d09c55af",
		["Warlocks, eh.  Well, you didn't hear it from me, but I've heard rumors that those types gather at a bar called the Slaughtered Lamb in the Mage Quarter.  "] = "f05de425d7bd02752037b8477cf01b53",
		["Looking for some training, eh? I could train you better then anyone in Stormwind but the guard prohibits it. I guess you will have to settle for one of those has beens hanging out around the Barracks or at the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town."] = "cd7fa3fdce25e94d80b36771810f1e93",
		["Tucked away in the Mage Quarter, there is a little shop called Alchemy Needs.  You're bound to see all sort of strange shops on your way through the Mage Quarter, but if you stick to the outer rim you'll be sure to find it."] = "8651024fca6f7bd42a0336d52e7d69fc",
		["You mean you can't smell the smoke of the Dwarven forges from here?  Well, you will be looking for Therum Deepforge if you want to learn blacksmithing.  He's over in the Dwarven District which is just north of the Cathedral Square."] = "a3a18a74f32a8ebab3109103db8d0fd5",
		["There's a great cook who works at the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town.  I've watched him use a knife when he cooks and just between you and me, I don't think he's always been a cook.  Don't get me wrong... if you still want to learn, he's the best we have."] = "af66b0b5d2d42f34571240ac0c887807",
		["Ah, you're looking for Lucan Cordell.  He runs a shop on the outside of the Magic Quarter on your way to the Stockade.  "] = "e3f9bcedb2188218c92b8b8fb1e8eb6a",
		["Hey, that reminds me, I need to have my rocket boots repaired.  Word to the wise my friend, rocket boots and gryphons don't mix.  Oh, but you need directions...  just head on over to the Dwarven District, you'll find Lilliam Sparkspindle towards the back."] = "bb3fee63f3293484e591674a691d3c88",
		["No better place to learn First Aid than under the watchful eye of Shaina Fuller at the Cathedral of Light.  To get there, just look for the yellow rooftops, or the towering spire of the Cathedral itself which you can see from almost anywhere in the city."] = "b1be3018807cc2da500145c8c2b10794",
		["That bum Leland... all he does is sit out on the dock outside the Trade District and fish all day.  I sure hope he's good at it for all the time he spends fishing.  If you want to learn, why don't you go talk to him?"] = "2472ef40c4054390e47d26a2790dcef8",
		["There's nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that's what the night elves tell me.  I'm not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I'm sure Tannysa could help you out.  She's over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs."] = "42747362bb8e6d2164d7e79747248058",
		["You're into leather, eh?  Sounds like you should talk to Simon Tanner over in Old Town.  He runs a shop there called the Protective Hide."] = "02b8fd48e20c73453938adc9f4995c2c",
		["Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he's here, he's probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District."] = "64070f95813e914bdca6f15e390c919e",
		["You know, I could run an orc through or slice up a troll.  I could even carve my initials in an ogre's flank, but I just can't stand to skin an animal.  Go figure, eh.  Well, if you have the stomach for it, then go see Maris Granger at the Protective Hide in Old Town."] = "c7ce82c152a63bc669f1d309ce17f9bd",
		["A tailor is it?  Well, if you hang out here long enough you'll eventually hear word of mouth about Georgio Bolero.  He's been setting the trends for some months now.  If you wish to learn from him, you can find him over in the Mage Quarter in the outer rim."] = "9cba4dc5407b5b21f860b325ab149a86",
		["What do you need directions to?"] = "2402ec9453525b4ec16e1180457c7cfb",
		["It is located in the Trade District citizen.  It is nearly straight on from the entrance of Stormwind."] = "568c01f3e19d99d5f41ea3aac2056ebe",
		["The Bank of Stormwind is located in the Trade District just northwest of the city gates. Here, let me show you on your map."] = "8fedf8298f3edb222d5b5f4355c58675",
		["You don't have the stomach for the gryphon ride, huh.  Well lucky for you, we have an alternative where you can keep your feet on the ground... more or less.  It's the gnomish mover of people, the Deeprun Tram.  Conveniently located in the back of the Dwarven District."] = "b8a17986e4d6330f2e74f8f8a53c0d86",
		["There are many establishments where you can get a drink in Stormwind, but only one will let you spend the night. Head over to the Gilded Rose in the Trade District. I've heard the cost of a room is reasonable and the sheets are clean. "] = "44af32f368e03c09b89fe9f87be3875e",
		["You can find the gryphon master on the northeast rampart overlooking the Valley of Heroes."] = "f5c1db946eb2f4fba13e922275d9fb95",
		["You can find Aldwin Laughlin at the Stormwind Vistor's Center in the Trade District."] = "53cfbdba892d116c2e03388c9fd6d5d0",
		["There is a mailbox located conveniently right between the Stormwind Bank and The Gilded Rose Inn in the Trade District."] = "bb63ff9d75c7726f1d06e21fe2021b8b",
		["Jenova Stoneshield over in the Dwarven District is the one you're looking for.  She tends to hunters' pets while they seek training from her father."] = "9654c77653b91d446f531295982fbec7",
		["Woo Ping's stamina is simply astounding.  Watching him practice his weapon techniques for hours on end, I felt sorry for the practice dummy afterward.  I can't think of anyone better suited to train you in armed combat."] = "312810e5deb14cd60aa19428f7f51227",
		["All of a sudden you're a 'Defender of the Alliance' are you?! Well, I suppose you'll be wanting to head to the Champions' Hall now. It's over in Old Town, but they won't let you in unless you're an officer, so you might just have to settle for talking to Officer Areyn outside. Move along now."] = "33278f8101e800c93fc3d2385cfed699",
		["Which battleground are you interested in?"] = "481f209702cc74fc87fe4569d25b276b",
		["Which class trainer are you looking for?"] = "7e357056bac5b73342ac2bee0458e300",
		["Which profession trainer are you looking for?"] = "ce83ae92effc9c6509cef60c5f919389",
		["Then it is Thelman Slatefist that you wish to speak to. You can find him in the presence of the King at Stormwind Keep."] = "bcfcce27aafd9e54ef3d2fcdb27f4139",
		["In the King's audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers."] = "9ff1ef7f7918452a7571c3f770ab4e14",
		["Indeed, Silverwing Hold is in need of your assistance. Speak with Elfarran in the audience chamber at Stormwind Keep."] = "ab67b49961ce98725cccb8a6b0e8e7ef",
		["Well, you can find Theridan or Maldryn by the moonwell in the Park.  Just head to the western area of Stormwind, north of the Mage District, but west of the Cathedral Square."] = "2c1e9110dff51f5d1d491b13523c5989",
		["Thorfin Stoneshield came to us all the way from Ironforge to bring us his expertise in hunting.  If you don't mind breathing the smoke filled air of the Dwarven District then you'll find him at his house in the northeast area of the district."] = "8c8ac67be8a32d83d11e1119cbe8b9f8",
		["The magi congregate in the Wizard's Sanctum in the Mage Quarter. Quite a tower they have there. Makes our barracks look like peasant hovels."] = "338c8fab07f57033e48217d5973c15df",
		["If you are looking to become a mighty paladin, there is no better teacher then Lord Grayson Shadowbreaker. He can be found in the Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square."] = "2d22a7afddcc8d88b9c1353ae28daf09",
		["The Cathedral of Light in Cathedral Square is home to the priests of Stormwind. There you will find High Priestess Laurena."] = "bb897a746e8a30c2b211e9076b6a286d",
		["You want to talk to Osborne then. No finer teacher of the stealth arts than him in Stormwind. Look for him over in Old Town."] = "5079ccedcf83df1e6554116dbaa337bd",
		["What? I don't know of any warlock trainers in Stormwind. Although... There have been some sightings of demonic activity over by The Slaughtered Lamb in the Mage Quarter. I suppose you could check there."] = "f6a52f523eecff532c9530eae7d0e89a",
		["Warriors can usually be found either at the Pig and Whistle Tavern or the Barracks in Old Town. Tell ya though, the tavern is probably a better place look."] = "9434f3b21efa2de084243d600d530ff5",
		["If you need training in alchemy, there is only one place in Stormwind you need to go... Alchemy Needs. You can find it in the Mage Quarter along the outer rim of shops."] = "7034523efe4bfc8203b790a1d127dca2",
		["Therum Deepforge is the dwarf you want to talk to. One of the finest blacksmiths around if you ask me. You can find him in the heart of the Dwarven District."] = "a4956fb4f50c46eaea4f68dd50ceb194",
		["If you are looking to become a great cook, venture over to the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town and talk to Stephen Ryback. That man knows how to cook up a rack of ribs like no other.Man... now you got me hungry for some of his famous ribs. Don't count on him teaching you that recipe though!"] = "dbe19e29f297c8e1fb35a95e50f89466",
		["Lucan Cordell has a small shop on the canal by the Stockade. I am sure he will be able to teach you the art of enchanting."] = "91e3f367dbb0e83b362a5880d1271dc4",
		["Stormwind's resident engineer trainer is an ingenious gnome by the name of Lilliam Sparkspindle. He can be found in the back of the Dwarven District."] = "05e90b70ee82c6ab15e68fec597454c2",
		["The Cathedral of Light is the center of all the healing practices of Stormwind. There you can find Shaina Fuller to help you learn this craft."] = "fd43bf9ef9a4ea5b42ea21a6017c205b",
		["Nothing like spending a day down at Crystal Lake fishing. Arnold Leland is the man that taught me. You can usually find him out on the dock in the Canal District just fishing the day away. Oh, and don't believe any of the stories he tells you about monsters in the canals either."] = "852f678dbc06d3601bdf168e7032735a",
		["You can find Tannysa standing outside Alchemy Needs in the Mage Quarter."] = "356b1700581f2c27333ab266a26bb077",
		["Want to learn leatherworking, eh? Simon Tanner would be able to teach you. He can be found in Old Town at the Protective Hide."] = "52ef93000b10574ffb40f6f451597e26",
		["Gelman Stonehand would be the one to talk to. I think he has a house over in the Dwarven District but I can't remember exactly. I would check over there."] = "8f8f48c440d58b1a783b868dd9222e74",
		["You are gonna want to head over to Old Town and drop by the Protective Hide if you are lookin' to learn skinning."] = "6f55eb7e6eebe144bc957790dae41464",
		["Duncan's Textiles employs one of the finest tailors in Stormwind, Georgio Bolero. Look for the shop over in the Mage Quarter."] = "8706ad14fe81bd7bfe9d6986ff68ed63"
	},
	["Huldar"] = {
