	},
	["Chaw Stronghide"] = {
		["Meat, skin, bones... a good hunter lets nothing go to waste. Every scrap of leather can be salvaged, perhaps to reinforce an ally's armor. Thus, each of us is strong alone, but together we become invincible."] = "f13238d0343549166ee185d5c7b13512",
		["You have outgrown any teachings I could offer. Go with the blessing of the Earth Mother. Seek out the tauren Tarn in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff's central plateau. Be guided by his wisdom."] = "e5c3faa7754d65e972344cb259b1aec1",
		["We live and die, and the land remains, eternal, unmoved by our passage. Thus, land cannot belong to us, $n. Instead, we belong to it. Therefore we protect the land, for without it we cannot hope to survive."] = "9802c328fee5a83bc01704102bf807c7"
	},
	["Bluffwatcher"] = {
		["You may shed yourself of your worldly possessions at the Thunder Bluff Bank on the lower rise."] = "bb2889c7bfa57a143417bd9b1f197fc1",
		["Ah, to soar with the great birds of the sky.  Seek out Tal at the top of the Winder Rider Roost.  He will steer you toward where you're going."] = "a71221b80997e8993fe99d8f65940c87",
		["A fellowship of kindred spirits can be a powerful force.  Krumn will help you to achieve this.  You will find him at the Thunder Bluff Civic Information center on the lower rise next to the lifts."] = "7428818296fb57ab2ba6a762f2e0d2d1",
		["Innkeeper Pala will help you rest your body and spirit.  You can find her in the building just south of the bank on the lower rise."] = "a76e86e6fc61fee2e4a3508cf1d715f5",
		["I believe I noticed a new shipment of mail being delivered not too long ago.  You'll find the mailbox just outside the Thunder Bluff Bank on the lower rise."] = "4953668f5dcca129474b758d1d23b145",
		["The auction house can be found on the central spire of Thunder Bluff.  Search near the bottom of the Windrider's Tower. May your ancestors watch over you."] = "a4a9ad83a2b44afa7328bfec39dea3c7",
		["None are as skilled in the use of weapons as Ansekhwa.  It is said that he is guided by the spirits of the finest warriors of our honored ancestors.  Seek him out on the lower rise and he will teach you what you want to know."] = "4113d427578d33dd0d7cc5960d9e551b",
		["The concern that you show for the welfare of your animal companions is commendable.  Bulrug, on the lower rise, can help you with that.  Seek him out between the bank and the inn."] = "d7325e94b3d82c25fc436cfe7d51f3f0",
		["There is one that I know of here in Thunder Bluff that can aid you in your journey to Alterac Valley. On the Hunter Rise look for Taim Ragetotem. May you find what you are looking for $n."] = "32652d64d7ec3c956ec22966227d3aad",
		["You wish to aid The Defilers in their fight against The League of Arathor in Arathi Basin?  Very well, you should ask Martin Lindsey for his assistance then.  Look for him in the Pools of Vision."] = "da5ea3194230fd515aa40fc906d898ab",
		["Such needless strife, but if the elves of Silverwing Hold will not speak to us in peace, then what alternative do they leave us? Seek out the aid of Kergul Bloodaxe on the Hunter Rise to get to Warsong Gulch."] = "7b590df5fa47f42b00a668a61d2d41b9",
		["Greetings honored one.  Turak Runetotem and the other druids have been expecting you at the Hall of Elders on Elder Rise."] = "5756887f0cd1cbab07deea21bfd1aeb8",
		["Any friend of the animals is a friend of mine.  The Hunter's Hall is what you seek.  It sits atop the Hunter Rise."] = "cd34633c29559796c6ebc619f7cdc14a",
		["Very sad to think what has befallen those poor undead souls.  You can find Archmage Shymm reflecting near the Pools of Vision under the Spirit Rise."] = "625f49a102fa08e5850ceb7e193dfaaf",
		["Despite their tragedy the Undead have come all this way to aid us.  I only hope that we can be as helpful to them.  Seek out Father Cobb near the Pools of Vision under the Spirit Rise."] = "90d649ee3e1d08c27a8665c6bdeff359",
		["The Earth Mother calls and you answer.  You will find the Hall of Spirits on the Spirit Rise."] = "dfd2bbc7b4882c8ae2435868f54dce8f",
		["Strong of body and spirit.  There can be no stronger combination!  Find your destiny with Sark Ragetotem in the Hunter's Hall."] = "9f80018ebca95bca3d012c9885917333",
		["The herbs found in nature can be a powerful ally when combined with respect.  You will want to seek out Bena at her alchemy shop on the middle rise to further your training."] = "599c6d8be27d0c47d6ed586b58d5e540",
		["Metal, as with all things, should be used in balance with nature.  Karn Stonehoof has a smithy setup near the pond on the lower rise.  Seek out his wisdom."] = "e6ee92e9034e719f370e30f576c15eda",
		["You honor the spirits of the animals you must slay by not letting them go to waste.  Aska Mistrunner will show you how.  She has a kitchen on the high rise."] = "9e2f8a46117e84f56a1520a66a6bde35",
		["The profession of Enchanting displays the cycle of destruction and creation that is at the heart of nature.  Teg at the Dawnstrider Enchanters on the middle rise will show you how."] = "c88c9780cf6c0a23744737daab1c43fe",
		["Life is a struggle, and the saying that which does not kill you makes you stronger is not always true.  Sometimes wounds act slowly, which is why we have bandages.  Pand Stonebinder of the Spirit Rise can teach you the art of First Aid."] = "4d9ce77b1fd1d043523dd81e104c633b",
		["Kah Mistrunner at Mountaintop Bait & Tackle on the high rise will show you the way to find inner peace and serenity while fishing for your next meal."] = "c00a4b671e155d6fa7a2d4aa63e871fb",
		["Nature provides all that we need.  Speak to Komin Winterhoof at Holistic Herbalism on the middle rise."] = "0e3a1c24f70f1c359a96057de011b71d",
		["There is a symmetry in the idea of the hide of your enemy providing you with protection.  To further your leatherworking skills look for Una inside the Thunder Bluff Armorers on the middle rise."] = "a1d048a682603a6da0676d45f85019cb",
		["The Earth Mother holds many secrets and Brek Stonehoof can help you to discover some of them.  You will find him on the lower rise at Stonehoof Geology."] = "9c03014605b27c25c059f0223bc21ad6",
		["Every scrap used makes us less wasteful and brings us closer to the Earth Mother.  Mooranta can show you the way.  Seek her just outside the Thunder Bluff Armorers on the middle rise."] = "1697153761e0b67c57f1cdd4dc2f2c12",
		["Clothing the tribe is as important a job as any other.  You should look for Tepa inside Thunder Bluff Armorers.  She has a natural way with the needle."] = "63954ad79a181f4bdebcb1e87ea78d14",
		["What are you looking for?"] = "b3d11178772212cc804676804bb92ca1",
		["The Thunder Bluff Bank can be found on the lower rise."] = "625203147fa733c66de63ce3f3252013",
		["The Wind Rider Roost is atop the totem stairway in the center of town."] = "16b85a7fda02544a6b24467f4130d30f",
		["Krumn is the bull you are looking for. He can be found on the lower rise at Thunder Bluff Civic Information."] = "0c6cb2a334460da852eecdbb7a3eb5c1",
		["Look for Innkeeper Pala in the building just south of the Thunder Bluff Bank on the lower rise."] = "8f087943366a3acf764b32af4c3ded23",
		["You can find a mailbox just outside the Thunder Bluff Bank on the lower rise."] = "0be0166409128e852e0cf07097c3b1cc",
		["It is found on the lowest section of Thunder Bluff.  Search near the bank.  It is not far from there."] = "959837cc6b3520206fd7ffcd50a3fc7a",
		["Ah, you seek the wisdom of Ansekhwa.  Look for him on the lower rise at Thunder Bluff Weapons."] = "1289a558c033b0924050a149cd96fe87",
		["It is the assistance of Bulrug that you need.  You will find him outside on the lower rise standing between the inn and the Thunder Bluff Bank."] = "5249bd4ce3fc5b36c84b65c6cdbaac96",
		["And to which battleground do you wish to journey?"] = "1d738815ffbfa1178b5cebf27d5e3cf0",
		["Which trainer do you seek?"] = "c5fec459a17d0b54dc8cfb9f0c9066ae",
		["Which profession?"] = "4a850dc32d00c265e503622c595cebf4",
		["Then it is to Taim Ragetotem that you must speak. Seek him out on the Hunter Rise."] = "b26bc8fc22a99ad20945a9589f5b955d",
		["You may seek out Martin Lindsey inside the Pools of Vision, underneath the Spirit Rise.  He will assist you on your way to Arathi Basin."] = "3de798b62a6a7c9477fb4ead6227ff5c",
		["Kergul Bloodaxe on the Hunter Rise stands ready to help you get to Warsong Gulch."] = "8dd5ae8dd52efbfbadf578cc9ba63982",
		["Seek out Turak Runetotem in the Hall of Elders on the Elder Rise."] = "f32f1f8317df644d79d3324fc75752ef",
		["Ahh, you will need to make your way over to the Hunter's Hall then. Several great hunters like Holt Thunderhorn can be found there on the Hunter Rise."] = "ec41eb4745bf50e326e8e13f25e45b8f",
		["A follower of the arcane are you?  Hmph!  Very well then... you can find them around the Pools of Vision underneath the Spirit Rise."] = "337db40ce448a7dc218d2910d441596a",
		["Father Cobb will be the one you want to talk to. He can be found under the Spirit Rise in the Pools of Vision cave."] = "764977ab49461a0e2f73e5c89e64d7bb",
		["The Hall of Spirits is where our shamans call home.  You can find it on the Spirit Rise.  May your ancestors watch over you."] = "26cdb9ef81f934c56123ecd5f8f82223",
		["Aspiring to join our ranks one day?  Sark Ragetotem can help you on your way.  He's in the Hunter's Hall."] = "da0f47520f4f0e59ff8825cae6d258b6",
		["Then head over to Bena's Alchemy on the middle rise and talk to Bena herself.  She will be able to help you master the art of potion brewing."] = "9c3a8733672857571a79608e45334e15",
		["Looking to learn how to work an anvil and hammer, eh?  Karn Stonehoof can teach you how.  He has a smithy set up on the lower rise by the pond."] = "b3ac26184e7b679b5f3a5fd050ceed51",
		["There is no finer cook in Thunder Bluff than Aska Mistrunner.  Mmmmm, I can smell what she is cooking from here.  Head over to her kitchen located on the high rise.Drat... now I am hungry."] = "f62291a619a18dcacc69b5f64e8dc599",
		["Check out Dawnstrider Enchanters on the middle rise then.  Teg will be more than happy to help you in whatever way he can."] = "9daecfcdaaa5812a8e8e882f46b515a2",
		["First Aid is always a nice skill to have.  Many a time during battle has it saved my hide.  Visit Spiritual Healing on the Spirit Rise.  Pand Stonebinder can teach you all you need to know to save your hide as well."] = "404195be7635731d800fe49c72496fde",
		["Don't blame you for taking up fishing.  Mulgore has some the best fishing spots in Southern Kalimdor and Mountaintop Bait & Tackle on the high rise has all of the gear you'll need to take advantage of it.Tell Kah Mistrunner that I sent ya!"] = "fedcf5e7226755c1e4b423ea45d0b484",
		["Komin Winterhoof at Holistic Herbalism is the one you want to talk to then.  He can be found on the middle rise."] = "83473bcdaf1b33eec50ef89c07b8748c",
		["Go see Una at Thunder Bluff Armorers then.  It can be found on the middle rise."] = "3ae20e97dad81c4d151a6d8c0b8448c7",
		["Brek Stonehoof can be found at Stonehoof Geology on the lower rise and can teach you the proper way to harvest precious ores and gems."] = "ab35cc7d314a40c2e9345c2f6bd27c2f",
		["Mooranta can help you learn skinning.  She can be found just outside the Thunder Bluff Armorers on the middle rise."] = "e7af07864db4b2551b191f075ac7869a",
		["Tepa is renown for her clothwork.  She can be found at Thunder Bluff Armorers on the middle rise."] = "2a0854c8bb2974724fa986a879759c63"
	},
	["Crystal Boughman"] = {
		["Cooking is a life long pursuit and I see we share the same passion!"] = "9894fe017afd5c82d452ec8f283f45f3",
		["Seek out Shandrina in Silverwind Refuge.  She can sell you the 'Expert Cookbook'."] = "efa6e9ddc589d11d0aeee639e21deb43",
		["Dirge Quikcleave of Gadgetzan is a master of the culinary arts.  To better yourself you will need to seek him out."] = "d25a7e0932a93ba447d43caf3968c467",
