	["Thotar"] = {
		["I train and guide young hunters in the traditions passed down many generations."] = "8a5b6aaedb16daf4e6daba6392ce1f16",
		["Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned?"] = "3a364a4573d4825a6795e3bb454069d4"
	},
	["Dhugru Gorelust"] = {
		["You know enough to be dangerous, but you still look like you need training to me $n."] = "f097ab331f582c2d79e805e164a7c169",
		["Your will is not strong enough to manipulate the forces we control $c."] = "5a92f47cf481eb3def2615b8693c94fc",
		["Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned?"] = "3a364a4573d4825a6795e3bb454069d4"
	},
	["Swart"] = {
		["The spirits have guided you to me. How may I be of service?"] = "7857c55cf19a633dd72142ae5b1f6578",
		["May the spirits be with you."] = "e7a2c0dc7f07afebb450c37adc691ede",
		["Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned?"] = "3a364a4573d4825a6795e3bb454069d4"
	},
	["Dwukk"] = {
		["I hear one comment about waterfowl, and you will be eating through a tube."] = "dcf73814792bd6614277533502604599"
	},
	["Harold Riggs"] = {
		["Your skill exceeds mine, though  I've heard that Old Man Heming in Booty Bay has copies of 'The Bass and You'.  That is sure to help you increase your skill."] = "13d2af5f294a07ae2cff1bf240fa32c1",
		["You will need to find Nat Pagle in Dustwallow Marsh to get any better than you are currently."] = "43ebea4a5129c29af35af2064eb93951",
		["I can teach you fishing skills."] = "b285645e1bdb1be37d7bfdc440534eec"
	},
	["Fremal Doohickey"] = {
		["The esteemed Doctor Gustaf VanHowzen can train you further.  He can be found in Theramore treating the wounded at the barracks."] = "9c8fb9d3a4f7df72d0d9fc92d703fc17",
		["I've heard it said that Deneb Walker, holed up in Stromgarde, has a book that is sure to help improve your First Aid techniques."] = "c0c9e599067b43084770b8a1fe8ce769",
		["I can train you in First Aid techniques."] = "7f7be7d9f859827d61dd9fcd5450e23e"
	},
	["Miao'zan"] = {
		["You got the look of someone wantin' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an' I train other folks to handle adventures for me."] = "2bddeb2204ae9a7ba01d834050d650f4",
		["Ready for another lesson? All right, then. First, relax. You gotta stay loose to stir a potion just right."] = "d7183ddb231e293b65e81976fe37b4d9",
		["You got questions, but they be too big for me to answer, $n. You be needin' to have words with the orc Yelmak in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He'll help you out."] = "3ccc9d3982a4f8dde9b5653bc0c2e796"
	},
	["Brave Ironhorn"] = {
		["We have no such place in the village.  The soaring heights of Thunder Bluff does though.  Head north up the road out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the base of the bluffs.  There ride the elevator to the top and speak with a Bluffwatcher.  May your ancestors watch over you."] = "c61c8d0a95bbdd9d8df4d9db44c53e73",
		["Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions."] = "e3b119cda97abe5ee10979d688350484",
		["There is a time and a place for all things, including relaxation.  On the west side of Bloodhoof Village Innkeeper Kauth maintains a long house for those who seek to rest.  You will find him there."] = "d0fbd1df4ebdde74721d6f5659827225",
		["Seikwa can take care of your animal friends when you have the need.  Seek her out in front of the inn."] = "38fd4c76a36f825f232997fc50761870",
		["The way of the Druid is sibling to the Shaman.  Gennia Runetotem is steeped in such knowledge.  Seek her out in the large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village."] = "6c2a1f69d196c4657a53b7c110c61e4c",
		["To learn to be one with Nature in the eyes of the Earth Mother, this is a matter of pride.  If your will is to learn the ways of the Hunter you must seek out Yaw Sharpmane at the north end of Bloodhoof Village."] = "21ee90ef1c873dcee3c9e57987f0dab4",
		["There is a wise one in the village who goes by the name Narm Skychaser.  He can continue your learning along the path of the Shaman."] = "af5b82f4f5903c5285a8c966bbd9396d",
		["If it is the way of the Warrior that you crave then you must seek out Krang Stonehoof.  You will find him in the southeast corner of the village at his training circle, often instructing his other students."] = "37885a7674244dd6e4cdeec2c68f5685",
		["Using the fruits of the Earth Mother to create potions to aid us in our eternal struggle is an honorable endeavor.  To learn of this you must travel north to our great home of Thunder Bluff.  When you arrive at the top seek out the assistance of one of the Bluffwatchers for more specific directions."] = "f53e995a55576c4dc433b9e11460ad87",
		["You desire to shape the bones of the Earth Mother into tools that will aid the Horde.  Good, good.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the elevator leading to the top of Thunder Bluff.  A Bluffwatcher there can give you further assistance."] = "e150bdb40bb2ad6d87a0d8460847996a",
		["My mouth waters just to think on it.  Pyall Silentstride is the finest cook in Bloodhoof Village.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village."] = "1c9e8d41e271bfa8a081921047868b8c",
		["Such wisdom is steeped in a mystery that can only be found in great Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to an elevator at the base of the bluffs.  Ride it to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for further assistance."] = "360397b474c43b7dcab78b62333d6ac1",
		["Bandages, anti-venoms and such things, these are the inevitable necessities of life on the plains.  Vira Younghoof can teach you this knowledge.  You can find her in the long house on the west side of Bloodhoof Village."] = "3134d4a4d8b645aeefba37aba15985b7",
		["Give a bull a fish and feed him for a day.  Teach a bull to fish and feed him for life.  Uthan Stillwater can teach you how to fish.  Seek his wisdom west of Bloodhoof Village along the banks of Stonebull Lake."] = "a50a61ff9211f062ebc4c78f9fccc5f6",
		["There are those that would teach you of Herbalism in the great home of Thunder Bluff away to the north.  Follow the road out of the village to get there and at the base of the bluff ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  There are many Bluffwatchers there who can direct you further."] = "201f3cba26808c32bb7ee62dfa628e09",
		["When we use the hides of the animals we must fell for food or protection we give honor to the Earth Mother and respect to the animal.  Chaw Stronghide can teach you of such things.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village."] = "e1efe823ee30b1c010852c13a53cb700",
		["I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Take the road out of the village and when you get there ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  Any of the Bluffwatchers should be able to help you from there."] = "e6cb4ccc587cd2a258b3ded78ae7a3f0",
		["Ah yes, Skinning.  There is no one finer in wielding a skinning knife than Yonn Deepcut.  You can find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village."] = "822d9c5197a44204042199ef7be11a36",
		["Tailoring you say?  Hmmm.  Ah yes, of course.  You'll need to head to Thunder Bluff, up north.  Take the path out of the village to get there.  When you arrive at the base of the bluffs ride the elevator to the top of the rise and speak with one of the Bluffwatchers."] = "aae10fc784263c4cb468d55cea4fd71e",
		["What are you looking for?"] = "b3d11178772212cc804676804bb92ca1",
		["Ah, you must go to the great heights of Thunder Bluff to visit one of those.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village.  At the base of the bluffs is an elevator that will take you to the top.  When you get there ask for further directions from one of the Bluffwatchers."] = "9e546e689233ec91191a43a7e36c67f5",
		["There is a Wind Rider Master in the great city of Thunder Bluff to the north.  Ride the elevator from the base of Thunder Bluff to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for further instructions."] = "b0b81da2b32d5fdbc23302be9744240a",
		["Innkeeper Kauth can see to your needs.  He can be found on the west side of the village in one of the long houses."] = "07ac0c881242c277b1b4be65bb1bb779",
		["Ah yes, it is Seikwa that you must find.  I believe I saw her last standing out in front of the inn."] = "4e99c32785b303ece538f803ff4fcb96",
		["Which trainer do you seek?"] = "c5fec459a17d0b54dc8cfb9f0c9066ae",
		["Which profession?"] = "4a850dc32d00c265e503622c595cebf4",
		["It is Gennia Runetotem's counsel that you seek.  You will find her in the large tent on the east side of the village."] = "dce81535973ad9064578c7dc07d654a1",
		["Yaw Sharpmane awaits you on the north edge of the village.  He can teach you the ways of the Hunter."] = "4c1b626c145d8077c5aa2db55852dcfa",
		["There is a large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.  You will find Narm Skychaser awaiting you there."] = "460e9ebf106048fdb04f6a2f81157b23",
		["Krang Stonehoof stands astride his training circle at the southeast corner of the village."] = "14d4e5dc44125fe42705f2ed118e5aed",
		["While we have no Alchemy Trainer here in Bloodhoof Village, there is one in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Follow the road there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions when you get to the top."] = "83cd87a9bd04fe41340d47a6a3863fb1",
		["There is a Blacksmithing Trainer in our great home Thunder Bluff to the north.  If you seek such knowledge then head there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions."] = "302142138778affead2a13087925b7b1",
		["You will find Pyall Silentstride inside the great tent in the northwest corner of the village.  He can teach you what you crave."] = "a234d4b10d5440d815b7b7172e8e8687",
		["Away to Thunder Bluff to the north is where your journey takes you then friend.  Once there seek out the wisdom of one of the Bluffwatchers who can tell you directly where to find whom you seek."] = "7c186bc25b44ca7d456a044d9c8671a4",
		["Vira Younghoof keeps her practice inside the long house on the west side of the village."] = "4f5f7ae4d60dbe2bd1bf43b0ad2e8786",
		["You are looking for Uthan Stillwater.  You will find him west of the village, fishing at Stonebull Lake."] = "50f0680942e77b17d91b589f7a3a11f1",
		["If you desire to learn the ways of Herbalism then it is to Thunder Bluff that you must go.  Follow the road north out of Bloodhoof Village and take the elevator to the top of the rise.  You can ask a Bluffwatcher there for further assistance."] = "52d1b670cce86f12a40bdf74b938d00d",
		["Inside the great tent at the northwest corner of the village is where Chaw Stronghide resides.  He will teach you what you must know of Leatherworking for now."] = "f68fe1ab41731a31f4c94d358440f989",
		["Hmmm, I think you will need to go up to Thunder Bluff to learn that.  Head north on the road out of Bloodhoof Village.  It will take you to the base of Thunder Bluff.  Ride the elevator to the top and you should be able to ask any of the Bluffwatchers there for further assistance."] = "bd7be540acfdb0455e58364636e73dda",
		["Yonn Deepcut can be found inside the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village."] = "951cf972b72fa8a3afed83790bceb3f0",
		["Unfortunately we do not have one who teaches Tailoring here in Bloodhoof Village, but you can find a trainer in Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of the village until you come to a set of elevators.  Take one up to the top of the rise and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for directions."] = "bbf8a87da18419b0d4c795a3f40babb6"
	},
