	["Brave Rainchaser"] = {
		["We have no such place in the village.  The soaring heights of Thunder Bluff does though.  Head north up the road out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the base of the bluffs.  There ride the elevator to the top and speak with a Bluffwatcher.  May your ancestors watch over you."] = "a07a2212481a399576ae9fe06a7f42c1",
		["Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions."] = "4cf39374ff7284a5b21cfc6b497fab6b",
		["There is a time and a place for all things, including relaxation.  On the west side of Bloodhoof Village Innkeeper Kauth maintains a long house for those who seek to rest.  You will find him there."] = "dbbfad5e8e294f119b31f17d69011c77",
		["Seikwa can take care of your animal friends when you have the need.  Seek her out in front of the inn."] = "fe99a91596ce335846112023b5594460",
		["The way of the Druid is sibling to the Shaman.  Gennia Runetotem is steeped in such knowledge.  Seek her out in the large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village."] = "1847fdcddef3e68075875dabef0e92ec",
		["To learn to be one with Nature in the eyes of the Earth Mother, this is a matter of pride.  If your will is to learn the ways of the Hunter you must seek out Yaw Sharpmane at the north end of Bloodhoof Village."] = "bf3892655633ebde448465a11f22228f",
		["There is a wise one in the village who goes by the name Narm Skychaser.  He can continue your learning along the path of the Shaman."] = "96139546004881a4294304b598ccc1bd",
		["If it is the way of the Warrior that you crave then you must seek out Krang Stonehoof.  You will find him in the southeast corner of the village at his training circle, often instructing his other students."] = "8561b5ef70805de6adb31be7df0beb1b",
		["Using the fruits of the Earth Mother to create potions to aid us in our eternal struggle is an honorable endeavor.  To learn of this you must travel north to our great home of Thunder Bluff.  When you arrive at the top seek out the assistance of one of the Bluffwatchers for more specific directions."] = "d0fa2619a007e29f2bcfcd0e5820bc3f",
		["You desire to shape the bones of the Earth Mother into tools that will aid the Horde.  Good, good.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the elevator leading to the top of Thunder Bluff.  A Bluffwatcher there can give you further assistance."] = "caa3688c962307b9b36884353c132080",
