		["Wulan in Shadowprey Village can sell you the 'Expert Cookbook'.  You will need that if you are to better yourself."] = "fc64c85b44749257ced7e34a940a1c64",
		["I can teach you how to cook!"] = "02987be90f767850ec8e9f572adbc4ed"
