	["Razor Hill Grunt"] = {
		["Yeah, I need to drop off some things myself.  Find it by heading north up the road to Orgrimmar and then ask one of the grunts there."] = "97ef6bb6459a1144372decbaa9f48cf8",
		["Can't you see I'm busy here?  Go north up the road to Orgrimmar and ask one of the grunts there.  You can't miss it."] = "1c4d2642c8dbafb4181f864054a4636a",
		["It's the big building in Razor Hill that's not the barracks.  Just talk to Innkeeper Grosk inside.  Got that?"] = "0e0f2725e989891e3b1b209b00b6c6ef",
		["Pets to take care of?  Just make sure you clean up after it!  Look for Shoja'my in front of the inn."] = "48c83d364a53dcd5c109f0279ac8ef23",
		["You're a hunter?  Well anyway, you'll find Thotar hiding from the sun inside the burrow at the southwest corner of town."] = "1481902397825d866ef861434702b11b",
		["That's troll business.  Look for Un'Thuwa in Sen'jin Village down south."] = "c09f94f3738012af627ee0ca8e140589",
		["Tai'jin is her name and you'll find her inside the barracks on the east side of Razor Hill.  She'll teach you to respect the gods.  Make certain that you show her the proper respect in return!"] = "c1a5522c52594a0f7383273d3f3d052b",
		["Why would you want to talk to Kaplak?  Nevermind.  Look for him on top of the burrow in the southwest corner of Razor Hill.  Just make sure that you keep your hands in your own pockets!"] = "ee3cff8c1213239b77f4d4ebd853af5b",
		["The Warchief brings change that will bring the Horde victory!  Look for Swart inside the barracks on the east side of town."] = "12e3380832481755103357bd8e4274e5",
		["Dhugru Gorelust is hiding behind the barracks on the east side of town.  Don't let me find out that you're in league with the Burning Legion!"] = "14afad71e6f43ebd4897a73651c3acd5",
		["Find Tarshaw Jaggedscar inside the barracks on the east side of Razor Hill.  Bring pride and honor to the Horde youngling!"] = "abc57ca8b9afe5891d11b478b0678324",
		["I hear that the trolls in Sen'jin Village have a potion maker named Miao'zan.  Look there."] = "252d6ae280f65f0827b5d62b61125ec5",
		["If you think you have the strength to pound good metal into weapons and armor for the Horde look for Dwukk next to the heated forge in the northwest corner of Razor Hill."] = "a2a68134eb6ead66dec0ff1ea26a3473",
		["Mmmmm food.  It's not too long of a run, but you need to head north to Orgrimmar and ask one of the grunts there."] = "f3be329749bffcc3c219519d18dac377",
		["I don't know of one of those around here.  Your best bet is to go to Orgrimmar to the north and speak to one of their grunts."] = "bad0c10059d93b0ba507c84cd442cad6",
		["Bah, that's goblin work!  Still, we have an orc here in Razor Hill that will teach you of such things.  Look for Mukdrak over near the forge."] = "fe9dd394ba942b3b46f201e888e073ce",
		["With all of the fighting we do of course we have a First Aid Trainer in Razor Hill.  Find Rawrk inside the barracks on the east side of town."] = "7a5f9a5c9e1af6b938e8d6fdb50d0765",
		["You're looking for Lau'Tiki.  You'll find him on Darkspear Strand out beyond Sen'jin Village to the south."] = "bf50f48d66f33ab47551f76d9412f407",
		["Flowers?  In this wasteland?  If anyone can teach you how to find them it will be Mishiki down in Sen'jin Village to the south."] = "96442a667845894083d0f2231cb79543",
		["To learn to cure leather and work with hides go to Orgrimmar to the north.  One of the Orgrimmar Grunts will be able to tell you the way to the Leatherworking Trainer."] = "480dcbe4bcc183db295991cfcf3e04ef",
		["Plenty of good mining to be had in Durotar, or so I hear.  So good in fact that we have a Mining Trainer right here in Razor Hill.  You'll find Krunn next to the heated forge in the northwest corner of town."] = "28da34a7dcc4893620bc3f9b17dbed6e",
		["There's one in Orgrimmar.  Go north and talk to one of their grunts."] = "e9ff9ec36b22276710cd8fde9ba0ca1f",
		["You can learn to sew up in Orgrimmar.  That's to the north.  Maybe one of the Orgrimmar Grunts can help you."] = "86bee557234aefc08dffcd603a3140f5",
		["What are you looking for?"] = "11f7e88f267338a9a8803626e9eb30be",
		["Huh?  You'll find the bank in Orgrimmar.  Head north up the road to get there and then talk to one of their grunts."] = "63df14ac6b0e503a51930d85a9b327bd",
		["You'll find the Wind Rider Master in Orgrimmar.  Go north up the road to get there and ask an Orgrimmar Grunt for further directions."] = "21b93df5517191e6ac378bd3f35e2e19",
		["I could use a drink and some rest myself.  You'll find it right in the northwest corner of Razor Hill.  Say hi to Innkeeper Grosk for me."] = "5a86f360c8ddfe8d0e1d5b8e50ba194b",
		["Shoja'my is over in front of the inn.  Now move along, I'm busy."] = "95ec5023f7dcbcb96b665624348b5662",
		["Which trainer do you seek?"] = "bb48a6496b0f939b97d651fb87555c27",
		["Which profession?"] = "539255a3b21365ed1ab0beecd22e319f",
		["The Hunter Trainer's name is Thotar.  Seek him out inside the burrow on the southwest corner of Razor Hill."] = "e71cc318705554503a1fc94f2fb2cf27",
		["Speak with Un'Thuwa to the south in Sen'jin Village."] = "0dcfd534ad129cf3f8457b6c1054259a",
		["You're looking for Tai'jin.  Find her in the barracks on the east side of town."] = "e72ab783318fd9303c927b656da1917d",
		["Find Kaplak on top of the burrow in the southwest section of town."] = "3f06598ffd8c9999b7f3e6b16011dfc5",
		["You need to find Swart.  Look for him inside the barracks on the east side of Razor Hill."] = "96d985b616d9e1814e6fa750a01f0e85",
		["On the east side of Razor Hill, behind the barracks is where you will find Dhugru Gorelust."] = "470b3f07f965638e1e086daec3b41a7d",
		["Look for Tarshaw Jaggedscar in the barracks on the east side of town."] = "352ae89eeeaac61dcc6845cd9f983cbd",
		["Seek out Miao'zan in Sen'jin Village to the south."] = "1531e56848a97f6caf0707bde10714be",
		["That would be Dwukk.  Find him next to the heated forge at the northwest corner of town."] = "68932fb0ffa48a7c03ec6bce0aa873db",
		["Head north up the road to Orgrimmar.  You can ask one of the grunts there for directions to the Cooking Trainer."] = "bb526804502f2666b56f5808503d68f7",
		["There's one in Orgrimmar.  A grunt up there will know what directions to give you.  Just head north up the road here, you can't miss it."] = "0e41adb6a7e141e297a7a7af38a7a151",
		["There is an Engineering Trainer in Razor Hill.  He is called Mukdrak and can usually be found standing over near the forge."] = "88e7460445b466f2393737512b4cace7",
		["There's one of those inside the barracks on the east side of Razor Hill.  Look for Rawrk."] = "bab9ae7a3d5ab170b5e4373908683d46",
		["I've seen a troll named Lau'Tiki fishing down south at the Darkspear Strand.  That's just on the outskirts of Sen'jin Village."] = "f531065fd60a051974df176bb74830f1",
		["You're looking for Mishiki.  She has a hut to the south in Sen'jin Village."] = "788e53903ca8bd09c088bd1d27efa397",
		["You'll need to head to Orgrimmar for that.  Just follow the road heading out of Razor Hill to the north through the canyon and you'll come to it.  When you get there ask one of their grunts for further directions."] = "1c20bee54f940a7ee25ae9b08ddc5bc7",
		["Sure, sure.  We have a Mining Trainer right here in town.  Look for Krunn over in the northwest corner alongside the inn."] = "c63f56c09345cbf81c450bfc0e570916",
		["There's a Skinning Trainer in Orgrimmar.  To get there head north up the road out of Razor Hill.  Ask an Orgrimmar Grunt for directions when you arrive."] = "fa4b7059d45bf0250381ea6aab634c1f",
		["Then Orgrimmar is where you need to go.  The north road out of Razor Hill leads directly there.  Just talk to one of the grunts there and they can give you further directions."] = "a8f60edf1e35fe995876160fbe01d53e"
	},
