	["Strahad Farsan"] = {
		["The arcane only corrupts those who are weak. Keep up on your training, or you may find a similar fate."] = "7533bf57cdb44c24f4dde1a0d3b1909a"
	},
	["Acolyte Magaz"] = {
		["Listen to your elders, $n. If you are strong of will and dedicated, there is no power you cannot control."] = "1765419d6b9c3acf6645811f022be3f9",
		["The infernal is one of the most powerful demons a warlock could hope to have at $Ghis:her; side in battle. The creature is stong, well-armored, and delivers devastating blows upon any foe. If you were to choose to put the spirit of an infernal into your weapon, you would gain some of those benefits--greater health and regeneration and the like.$B$BIf you wish to know more about felhounds, then you should speak to Wytula across from me."] = "681f6cccd8057b61841523c8b34b27c6"
	},
	["Acolyte Wytula"] = {
		["Not all Forsaken are driven by Sylvanas' will, $n. Some of us are driven by true power--power we earn for ourselves."] = "ab4fb84e95b89dcfe001b8f105e6210b",
		["The felhound... a vicious creature indeed. It is not as physically strong as an infernal, but a wise warlock knows that brute force is not always the answer--if it was, you would have chosen the path of a warrior instead, wouldn't you?$B$BThe felhound draws upon the mana of its foes, using that and its quickness to overcome enemies. Its strength comes from the arcane and using that arcane power for its own ends.$B$BIf you wish to know more about infernals, then you should speak to Magaz across from me."] = "e6e07bb5b51d4f770a4eeeaabc9bb7de"
	},
	["Menara Voidrender"] = {
		["Kar Aman, $n. You look to be a strong $c--you would do well to mind yourself in this area. Touching things you know nothing about, or showing disrespect to your elders is just cause for punishment.$B$BYou may not respect me or my companions, but you will learn to respect our power if you prove foolish enough.$B$BNow, enough with the pleasantries, was there something I can do for you?"] = "449cc5ea8d119cbfc577afff5f666b6f",
		["Ah, a fellow warlock who has proven $ghis:her; worth to some degree.$B$BI am pleased to meet your acquaintance. My name is Menara Voidrender... and not without just cause.$B$BYou seem powerful and well-learned enough that other tools... more powerful tools... would be welcome and not foolishly imparted. If this is true, then speak to me further. If not, well then, you know your way  back to the docks and off into the ocean."] = "4b606854cf99d129051fcd9c29d2c9e2",
		["Have you spoken to either of my acolytes inside the tower yet, $n? We cannot complete your orb until you've done one of their tasks. Speak to them now, if you're ready."] = "50f36dcd4a09a1faf4becc16a0525cdf"
	},
	["Innkeeper Janene"] = {
		["Welcome to my Inn, weary traveler. What can I do for you?"] = "db570f1f51f6fd3b1a42e5953bafd049",
		["No, I'm not, but lots of others are looking for love.  You should buy my love tokens, put on some cologne or perfume, and then pass them around!"] = "54899ff43d9fa3680bd5231fd54eae44",
		["Are you interested in exploring one of these dungeons?"] = "9211a5a83384bc6bf667f9e87661f2b5",
		["If you put on cologne or perfume, then you'll see who is amorous.  Those are the ones who accept love tokens... and offer a gift in return.$B$BBut remember: to give someone a love token, you have to smell just right!  Men like the scent of perfume, while women prefer cologne."] = "8e4dcb74091e2e615d506f3ec7d147ca",
		["Love tokens are small messages of affection you can give to amorous town and city folk.  Such people will reward you with a gift of adoration.$B$BOr, if you are already adored by another, then at the least they'll give you a gift of friendship."] = "cd40129110d4c4917a537fef57180329",
		["When you give love tokens to townsfolk, you'll receive different gifts in return.  Some of those you'll want to keep and use, but others can be bundled together and given to your favorite hero!  Visit Kwee Q. Peddlefeet to turn them in.$B$BKwee can be found near Bolvar, Magni, or Tyrande."] = "0838f3fe0e3c17a16a7ff7d504eec929",
		["When you give love tokens to townsfolk, you'll receive different gifts in return.  Some of those you'll want to keep and use, but others can be bundled together and given to your favorite hero!  Visit Kwee Q. Peddlefeet to turn them in.$B$BKwee can be found near Cairne, Sylvanas and Thrall."] = "9f470e7a9c62fa04faeb58fd3b1d6de9",
		["Ragefire Chasm can be found beneath the Shadow Cleft in the center of Orgrimmar."] = "b960d46bc6e1afd8a8048e75631efeb5",
		["The Deadmines can be found beneath Moonbrook in the south of Westfall."] = "cce75935af7718f82fcb4c3d13f23020",
		["The Wailing Caverns has its entrance at the Lushwater Oasis southwest of Crossroads in the Barrens.   "] = "58d9f5adb0c15d9e359abb8b40a54a91",
		["Shadowfang Keep is in southern Silverpine just north of Pyrewood Village."] = "17d13be0366794572061fb3fbb409ee6",
		["Blackfathom Deeps can be found at the north end of Zoram Strand along the coast of Ashenvale."] = "2d41c6e84da0f60aa520a4acc8919f87",
		["The Stormwind Stockades are found near the mage quarter in Stormwind."] = "8b063ee787233090be02c8d7fc8e58a7",
		["Razorfen Kraul can be found on the very southern tip of the Barrens on the west side of the road."] = "4855c8dab63ff7e92429d6df87b7b3cd",
		["Gnomeregan can be found in western Dun Morogh."] = "1e16c8ae0545b101ebc5ad4d9c69c248",
		["Scarlet Monastery lies in the hills northeast of Tirisfal Glades."] = "fe604977d24d31743e5481d5dcda2e88",
		["Razorfen Downs can be found on the very southern tip of the Barrens on the east side of the road."] = "ae45cd449d9b601c1faa2ad7d470e04a",
		["Maraudon is located in the middle of the western coast of Desolace, in the Valley of Spears."] = "b32b2b77a0839ff8c1415be4d2623dd9",
		["Uldaman can be found at the very northern end of the Badlands."] = "4324821d63a3f73937dd5abffe6fdf7f",
		["The ruins of Zul'Farrak are located in the northwestern corner of the Tanaris Desert."] = "5521f2e5d2e37d7012ea87b75badcb01",
		["Blackrock Mountain lies between Searing Gorge in the north and Burning Steppes in the south."] = "7beb3ee244d9c85c277537d4ba4a2fe1",
		["The Sunken Temple can be found in the center of a great lake in eastern Swamp of Sorrows."] = "75ed2903e0af8abe0c91025f4d1a631e",
		["The ruins of Dire Maul stand in central Ferelas."] = "863a0466292f35423e25fb6b1e18e872",
		["The ruined city of Stratholme lies in the Eastern Plaguelands to the north of the Plaguewood."] = "d9516bdeb534c80940a3be1f4600bf04",
		["The School for Necromancy known as Scholomance is on the ruined island of Caer Darrow in the Western Plaguelands."] = "4414ebedf67147d4801e58071b11c237"
