		["No, I'm not, but lots of others are looking for love.  You should buy my love tokens, put on some cologne or perfume, and then pass them around!"] = "54899ff43d9fa3680bd5231fd54eae44",
		["Are you interested in exploring one of these dungeons?"] = "9211a5a83384bc6bf667f9e87661f2b5",
		["If you put on cologne or perfume, then you'll see who is amorous.  Those are the ones who accept love tokens... and offer a gift in return.$B$BBut remember: to give someone a love token, you have to smell just right!  Men like the scent of perfume, while women prefer cologne."] = "8e4dcb74091e2e615d506f3ec7d147ca",
