	["Curgle Cranklehop"] = {
		["Hi there! I have a proposition for an adventure-seeker such as you, if you are up to the challenge!$B$BAlong with my invention, the Super Egg-O-Matic, I am hard at work aiding the druids with their campaign to save the hippogryphs. The birds are being affected by the evil effects of the Gordunni ogres inhabiting the ruins of Feralas, and their numbers are dwindling.$B$BI collect many different types of eggs.  Will you help and find some for me?"] = "a275ba473c8cc813159847ce18ab05ae",
		["In a place called Feralas to the west of here, the hippogryphs, long-time companions of the night elves, are in danger.$B$BI need you to rescue an egg from the ruins of Isildien, to the south, there. The Super Egg-O-Matic can analyze any egg brought to it and judge if it is likely to hatch. I then send the eggs along to the druids, safe from the Gordunni ogres' dark magics.$B$BPlease know, $n, some of the rescued eggs are bad eggs, and will never hatch."] = "49f43fc55d3582737bf410646dd05a11",
		["The Gordunni are a large ogre tribe that has control over considerable portions of forests in Feralas. Their dark magic seeps into the elements around them, damaging both the environment and the creatures that inhabit it.$B$BIf you do decide to travel to Feralas, please be mindful of these ogres -- they are quite nasty and many are able to wield powerful dark magic. "] = "0c6e66b796bf9729d8e0c65c441711d3"
	},
	["Tyrion"] = {
		["Oh, if I only had a tree branch to hold up in front of me. The guards would never see me then."] = "07770c2ddd975789dc652f86f33ee458",
		["You'll have to be patient with me, $n. I've got my Spybot inside working on a very delicate matter. I'll be with ya in a second.$B$BOh, and do me a favor, try not to let Lescovar see you... we're about to ambush him."] = "63ffa6f99e7677f212b497febf231182"
	},
	["Marvon Rivetseeker"] = {
		["I know, I know, I'm out here in the middle of nowhere!$B$BMy home is actually in Ratchet, but after crashing my zeppelin here, I thought I might as well start the research I came here to do!"] = "012cba0ea4f7f602188cc6eee3493caa"
	},
	["Kalin Windflight"] = {
		["To get down safely, I provide wings to those in need. "] = "095e13d4bc42c0c93f1c874f146d577f"
	},
	["Marli Wishrunner"] = {
		["The land of Feralas has been through much, $r. The earth, the trees, the creatures; they are all changing what Feralas is and will be.$B$BThe Twin Colossals above us remain as a constant, though, throughout all that has happened here..."] = "c848f51b35187eedb6b472e16b737fa5"
	},
	["Gregan Brewspewer"] = {
		["Hi there! The name's Gregan. What can I do for ya?"] = "7673b1e1c1aee85187bd33011e028202",
		["Sure thing, $n. You look like you can be trusted... Trustworthy! I can spot that a mile away...$B$BAnyway, back to what I was sayin'. Takes one Evoroot plant to make the Videre Elixir. The rest 'a the ingredients are trivial really, but the Evoroot, well, that can be a bit tricky to get."] = "f6ad8c672faab789040d554fb2b0b5a6",
		["Heh, heh... Quite the inquisitive one, aren't ya, $n? Well, here's what you need to do.$B$BNorth of here, in the old ruins, lives a very disagreeable gnoll by the name of Miblon Snarltooth. He guards the only Evoroot I know of, but he watches it night and day! Seems like he never even sleeps!$B$BWhat you can do, is bribe him. I can sell you some bait that he'll find tasty -- just put it down near him and that will distract him long enough for you to grab the Evoroot. Good luck!"] = "f3df391ade7879f97d794ce7af5fee06"
	},
	["Talo Thornhoof"] = {
		["Listen to the stories of an elder. $n. I have many to speak of..."] = "fe919449930ea179336d16a22b457806"
	},
	["Loramus Thalipedes"] = {
		["Can you see them, mortal? No... I did not think you could. Sighted but sightless - it is your gift and your curse."] = "f00870b9a046eed91eb4d0128f2dcee7",
		["In the age of war, Razelikh the Defiler served as the most fearsome of Lord Kazzak's lieutenants. When the Legion was defeated and Kazzak forced back into the Tainted Scar, Razelikh was tasked by his master to secure the Blasted Lands.$B$BWhile the Alliance fought petty battles with the Horde over territory outside of the Blasted Lands, Razelikh was uniting the differing Shadow Council sects and the brutish Dreadmaul ogres of the land."] = "d1af7e5517ae83c4c66dff4c1ff060ca",
		["Tragically, it was Thrall's wisdom that finally sealed the bond between the demon lord and his minions. It was Trebor's regiment that served as the catalyst to unite the demon lord, the shadowsworn sects and the ogres. The lure of nearly unlimited power and the granting of immortal shock troops to each respective leader sealed the deal in blood."] = "3726dcf3467f198a1a4e87d1350ab5d0"
	},
	["Trenton Lighthammer"] = {
		["Sul'thraze... the first time I heard the word uttered I was around your age. It meant nothing to me then, as it means nothing to you now. It was not until a warband of trolls coming from Zul'Farrak laid waste to the land that I understood... and feared.$B$BMany will tell you that the Splitblade of Suffering does not exist. That it's a myth; a rumor started to scare children 'straight.' But believe me, $r, it exists.$B$B<Trenton loses focus as he runs his hand across the jagged scar on his face.>"] = "e3c1562e647215741d05193021f0ffd6",
		["Split in two to form the one. The twin blades are bound to Zul'Farrak.$B$BSul'thraze reborn when the twins are found."] = "eea29ec80661302d9837db9ce53a5f5a"
	},
	["Bera Stonehammer"] = {
		["Where would you like to fly to?"] = "43540ff7458382b18eb66468d4ff2856"
	},
	["Bulkrek Ragefist"] = {
		["Where would you like to fly to?"] = "f686b3319d4af5004c6ee3403aea3f5e"
	},
	["Pratt McGrubben"] = {
		["I swear... if Quint tries to plant one more fishing grub on me, I'm going to hack down his tree with my not-so-rusty sword."] = "850288efe4dccb31f59391e76405f2b9",
		["Greetings $c -- if you're looking for leather goods and leatherworking supplies, you've come to the right semi-retired Paladin."] = "f4227fc6249932f3aa71dc28e89d87cf"
	},
	["Scooty"] = {
		["Hello, $n! I am master engineer, Scooty."] = "22c7e447f05eaff769b8cae4f2f6e0c9"
	},
	["Jangdor Swiftstrider"] = {
		["Welcome to Camp Mojache, brave $c.  How may I assist you this day?"] = "e40a5faf56ab3503cf189bed6d939698"
	},
	["Peter Galen"] = {
		["If you are here to hunt dragons, be my guest.  Where should I send my condolences?"] = "ecd8f490207aa548a5bde5be21a12239"
	},
	["Thorkaf Dragoneye"] = {
		["Your stench will attract every dragon for miles.  Tell me what you want, and quickly."] = "0249ed1756f9b7c5b5603fe23f7cb456"
	},
	["Sarah Tanner"] = {
		["Oh hi! My name's Sarah. What can I do for you?"] = "96e5d4c05909d0400168329dbcfac193"
	},
	["Brumn Winterhoof"] = {
		["The spirits told me you would come, that you would seek me for some reason, but that even you may not know that reason. So, do you know why you are here?"] = "f7eb9170dcfaa7e5f749986588580ced"
	},
	["Caryssia Moonhunter"] = {
		["The forest told me of your presence, but not why you were here. So, speak and enlighten me."] = "df2b761c9ca25bf3b7cf64efc2e5e6e8"
	},
	["Se'Jib"] = {
		["How you doin' mon!"] = "6e6caea26767043589a962c9cf10b835"
	},
	["Hadoken Swiftstrider"] = {
		["We must ensure the survival of this camp at all costs, $c!  Our enemies must not be given any quarter, for they would surely give us none were we to need it."] = "4d92317d28a869a2e22ffb04c657ac98"
	},
	["Quintis Jonespyre"] = {
		["Greetings, $c.  What may this humble servant of the Feathermoon Stronghold do for you today?"] = "9bd1329116de10f1184fdf255ad9ce76"
	},
	["Erelas Ambersky"] = {
		["Hello, $n. I train and care for young hippogryphs here; feel free to have a look around."] = "de300aecfe64e2c0dd5018d277df9334",
		["Druids are very sensitive to the plight of all creatures of the world. When it was found that these birds were in danger, we set up a system of rescuing them from the corruption of Feralas.$B$BA gnome named Curgle Cranklehop leads the affair; she collects the eggs and has them sent here, where I care for them.$B$BWe could always use more help for our cause, $n. Maybe you should head over to Gadgetzan and look for Curgle."] = "b19ba63af1bb1e807752e1767b2f0b9c"
	},
	["Tinkmaster Overspark"] = {
		["Greetings!  If you are here to access gnome engineering schemata, please have your gnome engineer membership card ready for verification."] = "899cfe761a6d79c6bdef221e3006e527",
		["I am Tinkmaster Overspark, and I am the chief architect for modern gnomish engineering principles in the world today.  It is my job to ensure that the power of invention continues to shine brightest from our arclight spanners than anywhere else!$B$BAlso, if you happen to know a good schematic for radiation elimination, we just so happen to be in the market for one right about now..."] = "7b5fc421a7124f4ac3dff2f5ae6ae20e"
	},
	["Brannock"] = {
		["Your skill exceeds mine, though  I've heard that Old Man Heming in Booty Bay has copies of 'The Bass and You'.  That is sure to help you increase your skill."] = "958a146c28400f9f9854e051f637dcfa",
		["You will need to find Nat Pagle in Dustwallow Marsh to get any better than you are currently."] = "2b445553ef42041e4fb79936cb957400",
		["I can teach you fishing skills."] = "a8d1f968e17b0d4c93ec75f0c6e5bfad"
	},
	["Kylanna Windwhisper"] = {
		["Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world."] = "d20db83d74494178c900eb4e6a102125",
		["Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill."] = "4856907d89101ae05bd0436fae2b8d02",
		["Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content."] = "7c26a76054cb4a99357c700203091c0b"
	},
	["Xylinnia Starshine"] = {
		["If you are seeking a truly rewarding pursuit, then a life of enchanting is for you!"] = "ce24b2e19a5dadecf917c1c4f4fd4ee8",
		["I know many things, stranger, but your knowledge rivals my own. Enchanters who wish to hone their skills further are known to travel to the Tower of Azora, where an artisan named Kitta Firewind resides."] = "eaade2c05b8910f296a765c4ce125adc",
		["Why don't we see just what you're capable of? If you complete the task I shall be happy to further your training! "] = "71b3c8878ca9d907574fab21af50df1a"
	},
	["Zjolnir"] = {
		["And a good day to ya, brave $c.  I know ya be lookin' for a fine steed.  There's no finer steed than a raptor under your reigns, lemme tell you $g mon : sis;!  Take a look at the ones I got to offer - bred from the fiercest stock anywhere."] = "2429cd9dc5d70eefd9b0308799bd8d64",
		["I'm sorry $g mon : sis;, but I won't be sellin' my raptors to someone who hasn't proven themselves to be exalted to the Darkspear tribe.  When ya make a stand and show yourself to be no less than exalted to us, then I'll make my raptors available to ya."] = "24ae77aab73cc857fb3bef8cc78e74d1"
	},
	["Xar'Ti"] = {
		["I can teach you the finer points of Raptor Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!"] = "3b10621402a461476ec028521e9fb4e0",
		["You need to be exalted with the trolls of the Darkspear tribe before I will teach you a riding skill, $c."] = "b3696ab9380b9a74f4dbfea7f6fda446",
		["I cannot be teachin' a Tauren to ride a Raptor."] = "991e17bc5cedbda60de365b1ffa51bb6"
	},
	["Binjy Featherwhistle"] = {
		["I can teach you the finer points of Mechanostrider Piloting, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!"] = "144516c0f69573ee3346350d1c8751f1",
		["I'd be wasting both your gold and my time if I were to teach you how to pilot a Mechanostrider, $c.  You're just too large!"] = "8793a1e3bacd16171e597a2e6e349f3b",
		["You need to be exalted with the gnomes of the Gnomeregan Exiles before I will teach you how to pilot a Mechanostrider, $c."] = "4a0058f7e90fd806fca67dea42c579d6"
	},
	["Milli Featherwhistle"] = {
		["Um... I think you're a little too big to ride a Mechano-strider there, $g mister : ma'am;.  You'd likely crush the finely tuned servo-balancers!"] = "65e354785b26bc4ab909aec7cd4f43eb",
		["If you have come looking for the gift of fast and safe mobility, then you have arrived at your destination!  This year's model of the new Mechano-striders have recently arrived, and I am ready to show you all they have to offer!"] = "299711f9bfc91cd6e18b4f2a9bc2baae",
		["Erm... I really don't know you that well, sorry.  I mean, as an authorized Mechano-strider dealer, I really only can sell my mounts to those people who are considered exalted amongst the gnomes.  If you ever are recognized as exalted to Gnomeregan, I'd be happy to show you what I have to offer."] = "19b68fb6acf9660f5027bc5ba4f9e9ad"
	},
