	["Argent Medic"] = {
		["I've got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way."] = "f21ac82310364bee548aaa65db9ae740",
		["I've got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way.$B$BIf you're infected with the maggot slime or ghoul rot, I might be able to help you."] = "69087ca98832c4d531ebd24380d184e3"
	},
	["Commander Stronghammer"] = {
		["Greetings, $r $c. I am Commander Stronghammer, the ambassador representing the Alliance here. If you have any questions concerning the status of Alliance collections for the Ahn'Qiraj war effort, $g lad : lass;, don't hesitate to ask."] = "f07f5e6d40044eae745e47cfd0b2ac14",
		["That's right, um, $g lad : lass;, all of the war materiel is being transported to Silithus and the last of it should get there within $2113w days. After that, we'll all just have to wait and see who puts forth a $g hero : heroine; to reconstitute the Scepter of the Shifting Sands and ring the gong on the Scarab Dais. Only when that occurs will the war begin to open the gates of Ahn'Qiraj."] = "698eb8f32440c4b3e71e2db100213268",
		["We are united in cause, $r. An ancient evil threatens to extinguish all life on Kalimdor and consume the world with its depravity... Its hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are the first and the last lines of defense against the armies of C'Thun. If we do not rise up and strike at our enemy, our enemy will surely destroy us.$B$BThe war effort needs you!"] = "ea8c9e4b80c9fb807cffa1aa88bd86b7",
		["A very good question, $c. When last I had heard, the Alliance had managed to smelt $1997w out of $1998w copper bars, $2002w out of $2003w iron bars and $2011w out of $2012w thorium bars needed for the war effort."] = "600752944f2ed7a5f2e5c2e398845f1c",
		["Let me see, let me see. I had those numbers here somewhere. Ah yes, here they are! To date, the Alliance has collected $2047w stranglekelp, out of $2048w needed. It also says here that we have $2053w of $2055w purple lotus and $2057w out of $2058w arthas' tears needed."] = "6a21e863d9f49ec0041bd59ac1f3f839",
		["Funny you should ask... I just received an update on that. Thus far, the Alliance has gathered $2060w of $2061w light leather, $2063w out of $2064w medium leather and $2069w of $2071w thick leather skins."] = "80b3888d40c7eca0d3c8b8f9d61f3ac7",
		["Bandages you say? Yes, well, if memory serves from the last time I was told, it would appear that the Alliance has created $2076w of $2077w linen bandages, $2082w of $2083w silk bandages and $2088w of $2090w runecloth bandages."] = "ac1fc16d38645b54c1f8b2109349f841",
		["That reminds me, I'm going to need to find something to eat soon. As to what the Alliance has been cooking up, I'm told that $2092w out of $2093w rainbow fin albacore have been packed away. As well, $2098w of $2099w roast raptor and $2101w out of $2103w spotted yellowtail have been prepared and are currently in cold storage awaiting transport to Cenarion Hold in Silithus."] = "1b0ce06896ec82f2b8d9de5f2bdfcecb"
	},
	["Warlord Gorchuk"] = {
		["Throm'ka, Horde $C, stand proud! I am Warlord Gorchuk, commander of the Horde's war effort. There are trying times ahead of us, but we shall prevail, as always.$B$BIf you have questions, you should ask them."] = "ff1113878810a7326aec257f03be15c6",
		["The time for war is almost upon us, $c! Both the Horde and the Alliance have finished with their preparations. All of our war materiel is being shipped to Silithus as we speak. I'd expect it all to arrive within $2113w days. When all is assembled there, the one who has completed the arduous task of reassembling the Scepter of the Shifting Sands will bang it against the Scarab Gong and open the gates to Ahn'Qiraj. Then battle shall be joined as has not been seen in ages!$B$BLok'tar Ogar!"] = "f6c0c1ea475d9aa33d7c2f43bb8f2ba6",
		["We stand together with the Alliance, $r. An evil, so old that the world has forgotten it, seeks to engulf us all; first on Kalimdor and then the rest of Azeroth. It is driven by a hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are all that stand in the way of C'Thun's armies. We will strike first and bring down the forces of Ahn'Qiraj. Let all of Azeroth quake at the combined might of the Horde and Alliance.$B$BThe war effort needs you!"] = "867569b880563887beb157cd19a1f51b",
		["Of the $1998w copper bars that we'll need, we have $2018w. The number for tin bar collections sits at $2005w out of $2006w needed. And, there have been $2008w of $2009w mithril bars smelted for the cause."] = "44b41addd3f8437df6055fc58b0a56d6",
		["I just received word on that. We currently have $2021w out of $2020w peacebloom, $2050w of $2051w firebloom, and $2054w out of $2055w purple lotus herbs requested."] = "23e117cdf828f64a8f7832003c53ad13",
		["Give me a moment; there are a lot of numbers to remember here. It looks like we have $2066w of $2067w heavy leather skins collected. As well, we have $2070w out of $2071w thick leather, and $2073w of $2074w rugged leather stockpiled."] = "5c6ee7053a94c92a28eaa92bf7f821d5",
		["Bandages? Why, do you intend to survive long enough to need them? Har! Very well, $r, I will tell you. Of the $2080w wool bandaged needed, we have collected $2079w. Also to date, we have taken in $2085w out of $2086w mageweave bandages, and $2089w of $2090w runecloth bandages asked for."] = "263b5382493c8292898a68606c67c3c9",
		["Food, now there's a subject that I can sink my fangs into! I am told that we have $2095w of $2096w lean wolf steaks, $2102w out of $2103w spotted yellowtail, and $2105w of $2106w baked salmon on ice and stored away."] = "a47ee7bcd6b3b8125ec6007fb1bbd6b9"
	},
	["Senior Sergeant Kai'jin"] = {
		["Hail, $c. I trust you are here to inquire on the Ahn'Qiraj war effort. We are going to need a great deal of assistance.$B$BThe war effort is a united effort between the Horde and Alliance to prepare for the impending war against the Silithid and their masters in Ahn'Qiraj. In Orgrimmar's Valley of Spirits, we are collecting a vast number of goods to create war materiel, and these gathering tasks are what we need your help with.$B$BCan I convince you to speak with our commander about helping out?"] = "17bbc17d735f1204b639e93017b4f12d"
	},
	["Master Sergeant Fizzlebolt"] = {
		["Unexpected that you are all capable of such organization. Both the Alliance and the Horde have completed their preparations for the Ahn'Qiraj War. Even as we speak the materiel is being shipped over to Silithus and should all arrive within $2113w days. Then it is up to the one who is going to reassemble the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to beat on the gong at the Scarab Dais and open the gates of Ahn'Qiraj. That is when the war will truly begin!"] = "8ca2008a454762fd014b24e00bac0365",
		["Well met, $c. I hope you are here to inquire on the Ahn'Qiraj war effort. We are going to need a great deal of assistance.$B$BThe war effort is a united effort between the Alliance and Horde to prepare for the upcoming war against the Silithid and their masters in Ahn'Qiraj. In the Military Ward of Ironforge, we are collecting all manner of goods to create our war materiel from, and these gathering tasks are what we need your help with.$B$BCan I convince you to speak with our commander about pitching in?"] = "715abbee6fe7adab32ccbe9ca9fc20d0"
	},
	["Thunder Bluff Commendation Officer"] = {
		["Greetings, $c - I'm a Commendation Officer acting on behalf of Thunder Bluff.  It is my duty to assist adventurers who have received Horde Commendation Signets.$B$BI accept signets in different quantities, but the most beneficial exchange for you is to hand in a set of ten at once.  I will enter your deeds into our records when you hand in your signets.  As a result, you will earn recognition from Thunder Bluff for your duty and service."] = "e546a36a7eeaabafa3ea21329d0ac9da"
	},
	["Guard Didier"] = {
		["Terrible thing, what happened to them mules... Metz is gonna have my hide for this failure."] = "3b7842ece739d108a318b6738cedbf47"
	},
	["Cultist Engineer"] = {
		["This cultist is in a deep trance..."] = "73f0462573697c404b28308bec6f882a"
	},
	["Argent Dawn Initiate"] = {
		["The battle is won. For the time being, the Scourge threat has been pushed back. Our resources can be channeled into aiding you, in thanks and preparation for the future."] = "ebde1b78097e360ae80271b45ac8ec9b",
		["The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle."] = "4d4e9052d3c36392e6211cb442ea3b1e",
		["The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle."] = "0973188afdf5745ee7a53c42da926c63"
	},
	["Argent Dawn Paladin"] = {
		["The battle is won. For the time being, the Scourge threat has been pushed back. Our resources can be channeled into aiding you, in thanks and preparation for the future."] = "4b36cae8ffab10bd243caafa37fd7ebd",
		["The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle."] = "fdaab9e2b8a9ef75ee889a83109b9758",
		["The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle."] = "b4933008c7c76fbea261d6b6ba7192ca"
	},
	["William Kielar"] = {
		["Don't be alarmed... while my gryphons may not be entirely whole, they will still carry you faithfully to your destination. Tell me... which tower do you seek?"] = "8c3e5d1b67a507ae3bf5d583b20cea89"
	},
	["General Zog"] = {
		["Lok'tar, $r. I am General Zog, ambassador of the Horde. I am here to keep you apprised of the progress that the mighty Horde is making in their efforts toward the Ahn'Qiraj War. What is it that you want to know?"] = "d2747cbf9e92ad97f5c16f908b596c77",
		["Unexpected that you are all capable of such organization. Both the Alliance and the Horde have completed their preparations for the Ahn'Qiraj War. Even as we speak the materiel is being shipped over to Silithus and should all arrive within $2113w days. Then it is up to the one who is going to reassemble the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to beat on the gong at the Scarab Dais and open the gates of Ahn'Qiraj. That is when the war will truly begin!"] = "558293036bc20ba9ec357e7955395f89",
		["We stand together with the Alliance, $r. An evil, so old that the world has forgotten it, seeks to engulf us all; first on Kalimdor and then the rest of Azeroth. It is driven by a hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are all that stand in the way of C'Thun's armies. We will strike first and bring down the forces of Ahn'Qiraj. Let all of Azeroth quake at the combined might of the Horde and Alliance.$B$BThe war effort needs you!"] = "867569b880563887beb157cd19a1f51b",
		["How many metal bars you say? As of my last update on the situation, here is what I know. The Horde has collected $2018w copper bars out of $1998w needed, $2005w tin bars out of $2006w and of $2009w mithril bars sought, $2008w have been gathered."] = "8caa274c49387b4edd0ba33ed966f6b7",
		["Last I heard the Horde had accumulated $2021w of $2020w peacebloom, $2050w of $2051w firebloom and $2054w out of $2055w purple lotuses."] = "c87aec42c0c1d25bbb47559200796d1d",
		["Leather skins? Yes, I just received some information on that. It would appear that of $2067w heavy leather needed, the Horde has collected $2066w. Also, $2070w out of $2071w thick leather and $2073w out of $2074w rugged leather have been gathered."] = "6fc4d0924029489ffd0a60e0ee958c21",
		["The Horde is stockpiling a great many bandages. So far $2079w out of $2080w wool bandages have been collected. $2085w out of $2086w mageweave bandages have been created. And $2089w out of $2090w runecloth bandages have been gathered."] = "a262f229e20203f5b92f45814fe50213",
		["You want to know about ration collections? Very well. Last I was told, the Horde had prepared $2095w out of $2096w lean wolf steaks. We've also packed away $2102w of $2103w spotted yellowtail and $2105w out of $2106w baked salmon needed."] = "c2a83d587c94ee4ec39e5ad2da461816"
	},
	["Field Marshal Snowfall"] = {
		["Greetings, $c. I am Field Marshal Snowfall, commander of the war effort here. We've a hard road to plow ahead of us, $g lad : lass;, so if you can help out, please do so. And feel free to ask questions."] = "ac0a0b581e16d91b9d2a09b564f6d6c3",
		["We've done it, $g lad : lass;! The Alliance and the Horde have completed gathering everything that we think we'll need for the Ahn'Qiraj War. Right now the final goods are being taken over to Cenarion Hold in Silithus and all of it will arrive within $2113w days. After that, some brave $g hero : heroine; is going to need to ring the Scarab Gong with the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to open the gates to Ahn'Qiraj. When those gates open, the war begins!"] = "e5b3d0a093a4c464534cd95408b3c863",
		["We are united in cause, $r. An ancient evil threatens to extinguish all life on Kalimdor and consume the world with its depravity... Its hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are the first and the last lines of defense against the armies of C'Thun. If we do not rise up and strike at our enemy, our enemy will surely destroy us.$B$BThe war effort needs you!"] = "ea8c9e4b80c9fb807cffa1aa88bd86b7",
		["Good question, $c. Last I was informed; we have managed to collect $1997w copper bars out of $1998w needed. Additionally, I am told that we have $2002w iron bars out of $2003w, and $2011w out of $2012w thorium bars requested."] = "81234ee743d3102e90bf455d5a474ae2",
		["Herbs, herbs, hmmm, let me see here. Ah yes, here it is. To date we have accumulated $2047w out of $2048w stranglekelp, $2053w out of $2055w purple lotuses, and $2057w out of $2058w arthas' tears needed."] = "6c50ab0ff636941be77f3f70ca2b8823",
		["I received an update on that just a moment ago. It looks like out of $2061w light leather needed, we have $2060w. As for the others, the report indicated that we've gathered $2063w of $2064w medium leather, and $2069w out of our $2071w thick leather quota."] = "530a831c03043cceba408219672180c6",
		["Collection of bandages is proceeding according to schedule. As far as linen bandages are concerned, we've gathered $2076w of $2077w. Silk bandages have been tallied at $2082w out of $2083w, and we have $2088w out of $2090w runecloth bandages needed."] = "cb739c796aa3b55fa68a388c2a9df332",
		["On the cooked goods front it would appear that we've managed to collect and store away $2092w rainbow fin albacore, out of $2093w requested. Additionally, right now we have in $2098w of $2099w roast raptor and $2101w out of $2103w spotted yellowtail in cold storage."] = "f66cbdf5f4c0994a74f1f4bca30e6850"
	},
	["Master Sergeant Moonshadow"] = {
		["Are you reporting for duty, $c? All of the war materiel for both the Horde and the Alliance is completed and being shipped to Silithus as we speak. It should all arrive in less than $2113w days. I hope that someone has found the different pieces of the Scepter of the Shifting Sands and put them all together."] = "f7a0177f1d58938bf2f5b7ff9fe23301",
		["Well met, $c. I hope you are here to inquire on the Ahn'Qiraj war effort. We are going to need a great deal of assistance.$B$BThe war effort is a united effort between the Alliance and Horde to prepare for the upcoming war against the Silithid and their masters in Ahn'Qiraj. In the Military Ward of Ironforge, we are collecting all manner of goods to create our war materiel from, and these gathering tasks are what we need your help with.$B$BCan I convince you to speak with our commander about pitching in?"] = "fa64bddf4571be9bf5ab8eda9ea581c3"
	},
	["Darnassus Commendation Officer"] = {
