		["It is the last night of the Lunar Festival.  May fortune be with you!"] = "ea6aed234baf22eb98af03d184469b13",
		["They put these lanterns out to commemorate the closing of the Lunar Festival."] = "7e9c620ca526252a37ea37761109af3c",
